site_name: Phase 2, Holmbury House and part Farmleigh House
description: As Phase 2 of the comprehensive redevelopment of the Loughborough Park Estate, the demolition of 105 dwellings currently contained within Holmbury House and three cores of Farmleigh House; and the erection of 95 new homes in two residential blocks (one ranging from five to eight storeys in height and one ranging from four to five storeys), highways and parking, associated landscaping, the provision of allotments, the erection of an electrical substation and all associated and ancillary development.
